---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Typography | Palo" description="用于展示 Markdown 常见元素在站点上的排版效果。">
	<main class="typography">
		<h1>Typography</h1>

		<p>这是一页用于直观查看 Markdown 常见元素，以及它们渲染后的 HTML 结构在网站中的表现。</p>

		<hr />

		<h2>Headings</h2>

		<h1>Heading 1</h1>
		<h2>Heading 2</h2>
		<h3>Heading 3</h3>
		<h4>Heading 4</h4>
		<h5>Heading 5</h5>
		<h6>Heading 6</h6>

		<hr />

		<h2>Paragraph &amp; Inline</h2>

		<p>这是一个普通段落示例，用于观察行高、字体颜色与间距。</p>

		<p>
			强调：
			<em>斜体</em>、<strong>加粗</strong>、<strong><em>加粗+斜体</em></strong>、<del>删除线</del>。
		</p>

		<p>行内代码：<code>const hello = "Palo";</code></p>

		<p>
			链接：
			<a href="https://astro.build/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Astro</a>
		</p>

		<p>图片（8:5 封面示例）：</p>
		<p>
			<img src="/covers/portfolio-aurora.svg" alt="Portfolio cover" />
		</p>

		<hr />

		<h2>Blockquote</h2>

		<blockquote>
			<p>这是一个区块引用示例。</p>
			<p>可以跨多行，方便观察缩进、边框、背景与字体对比度。</p>
		</blockquote>

		<hr />

		<h2>Horizontal Rule</h2>

		<hr />

		<h2>Lists</h2>

		<h3>Unordered List</h3>

		<ul>
			<li>Unordered item</li>
			<li>Unordered item</li>
			<li>
				Nested group
				<ul>
					<li>Nested item</li>
					<li>Nested item</li>
				</ul>
			</li>
		</ul>

		<h3>Ordered List</h3>

		<ol>
			<li>Ordered item</li>
			<li>
				Ordered item
				<ol>
					<li>Nested ordered item</li>
					<li>Nested ordered item</li>
				</ol>
			</li>
		</ol>

		<h3>Task List</h3>

		<ul class="task-list">
			<li><input type="checkbox" checked disabled /> Done</li>
			<li><input type="checkbox" disabled /> Todo</li>
		</ul>

		<hr />

		<h2>Code</h2>

		<h3>Inline Code</h3>

		<p>你可以在段落里插入 <code>inline code</code>。</p>

		<h3>Code Block</h3>

		<pre><code class="language-js">{`// Simple example
export function greet(name) {
  return \`Hello, \${name}!\`;
}
`}</code></pre>

		<hr />

		<h2>Table</h2>

		<table>
			<thead>
				<tr>
					<th>Feature</th>
					<th>Example text</th>
				</tr>
			</thead>
			<tbody>
				<tr>
					<td>Headings</td>
					<td># / ## / ###</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td>Inline</td>
					<td>*italic* / **bold**</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td>Lists</td>
					<td>unordered / ordered</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td>Code</td>
					<td>fenced block</td>
				</tr>
			</tbody>
		</table>

		<hr />

		<h2>Misc</h2>

		<p><sub>Subscript</sub> and <sup>Superscript</sup></p>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	.typography {
		max-width: var(--page-max-width);
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 3rem var(--page-gutter) 5rem;
	}

	.typography h1,
	.typography h2,
	.typography h3,
	.typography h4,
	.typography h5,
	.typography h6 {
		letter-spacing: -0.03em;
	}

	.typography p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.typography hr {
		border: 0;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
		margin: 2rem 0;
	}

	.typography code {
		font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas,
			'Liberation Mono', 'Courier New', monospace;
		font-size: 0.95em;
	}

	.typography pre {
		background: var(--card-bg);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: 0.95rem;
		padding: 1rem;
		overflow: auto;
	}

	.typography blockquote {
		margin: 1.5rem 0;
		padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
		border-left: 4px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.6);
		background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.08);
		color: var(--text);
		border-radius: 0.6rem;
	}

	.typography blockquote p {
		color: inherit;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.typography blockquote p + p {
		margin-top: 0.75rem;
	}

	.typography ul,
	.typography ol {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		line-height: 1.8;
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
	}

	.typography ul ul,
	.typography ol ol {
		margin-top: 0.35rem;
	}

	.typography .task-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding-left: 0;
	}

	.typography .task-list li {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.55rem;
	}

	.typography table {
		width: 100%;
		border-collapse: collapse;
		margin: 1rem 0;
	}

	.typography th,
	.typography td {
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		padding: 0.75rem 0.85rem;
		text-align: left;
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	.typography th {
		color: var(--text-strong);
		background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.08);
	}

	.typography img {
		display: block;
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 720px;
		border-radius: 0.95rem;
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
	}
</style>
